Paper: hep-th/0203174

Date: 2002-03-19

Title: On Decomposing N=2 Line Bundles as Tensor Products of N=1 Line Bundles

Authors: Fausto Ongay and Jeffrey M. Rabin

Comments: 7 pages

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 61 (2002) 101-106

We obtain the existence of a cohomological obstruction to expressing N=2 linebundles as tensor products of N=1 bundles. The motivation behind this paper isan attempt at understanding the N=2 super KP equation via Baker functions,which are special sections of line bundles on supercurves.